  754: init_per_suite(Config) ->
  755:     file:set_cwd(datadir(Config)),
  756:     ok = erl_tar:extract("xmlts20130923.tar.gz", [compressed]),
  757:     Dirs = ["ibm","japanese","oasis","sun","xmltest"],
  758:     [file:rename("xmlconf/" ++ Dir, Dir) || Dir <- Dirs],
  759:     [ok = erl_tar:extract(Dir ++ ".tgz", [compressed]) || Dir <- Dirs],
  760:     ok = change_mode(Dirs),
  761:     Config.
  762: 
  763: -ifndef(dont_rm_test_dirs).
  764: end_per_suite(Config) ->
  765:     file:set_cwd(datadir(Config)),
  766:     ok = rm_files(["ibm","japanese","oasis","sun","xmltest", "xmlconf"]),
  767:     ok.
  768: 
  769: -else.
  770: end_per_suite(Config) ->
  771:     ok.
  772: -endif.

  778:     code:add_patha(privdir(Config)),
  779:     Config.

  784:     ok.

 9902: %% Dir is a directory
 9903: rm_f_(Dir) ->
 9904:     {ok,CWD} = file:get_cwd(),
 9905:     {ok,FileList} = file:list_dir(Dir),
 9906:     file:set_cwd(filename:join([CWD,Dir])),
 9907:     rm_files(FileList),
 9908:     file:set_cwd(CWD),
 9909:     ? line ok = file:del_dir(Dir).
 9910: 
 9911: rm_files([])->
 9912:     ok;
 9913: rm_files([F|Fs]) ->
 9914:     case filelib:is_dir(F) of
 9915: 	true ->
 9916: 	    rm_f_(F);
 9917: 	_ ->
 9918: 	    ok = file:delete(F)
 9919:     end,
 9920:     rm_files(Fs).
 9921: 
 9922: -include_lib("kernel/include/file.hrl").
 9923: change_mode(Files) ->
 9924:     change_mode3(Files).
 9925: change_mode2(Dir)->
 9926:     {ok,CWD} = file:get_cwd(),
 9927:     {ok,FileList} = file:list_dir(Dir),
 9928:     file:set_cwd(filename:join([CWD,Dir])),
 9929:     change_mode3(FileList),
 9930:     file:set_cwd(CWD).
 9931: change_mode3([]) ->
 9932:     ok;
 9933: change_mode3([F|Fs]) ->
 9934:     case filelib:is_dir(F) of
 9935: 	true ->
 9936: 	    chmod(F),
 9937: 	    change_mode2(F);
 9938: 	_ ->
 9939: 	    chmod(F)
 9940:     end,
 9941:     change_mode3(Fs).
 9942:     
 9943: chmod(F) ->
 9944:     case file:read_file_info(F) of
 9945: 	{ok,FileInfo} ->
 9946: 	    Mode= FileInfo#file_info.mode,
 9947: 	    file:write_file_info(F,FileInfo#file_info{mode=8#00777 bor Mode});
 9948: 	_ ->
 9949: 	    ok
 9950:     end.
 9951:     
 9952: privdir(Config) ->
 9953:     proplists:get_value(priv_dir, Config).
 9954: datadir(Config) ->
 9955:     proplists:get_value(data_dir, Config).
 9956: 
 9957: datadir_join(Config,Files) ->
 9958:     File = filename:join([datadir(Config)|Files]),
 9959:     ct:log("File: ~ts~n",[File]),
 9960:     File.
